{"pageProps":{"problem":{"id":"t26-train-1","grade":"7","semester":"up","category":"一元一次方程","title":"针对训练1：裂项相消应用","difficulty":4,"tags":["方程","裂项"],"content":"解方程：$\\frac{x}{3} + \\frac{x}{15} + \\frac{x}{35} + \\cdots + \\frac{x}{2023 \\times 2025} = 1$","steps":[{"title":"解析","content":"分母序列为 $1\\times3, 3\\times5, 5\\times7, \\dots, 2023\\times2025$\n\n利用裂项公式：$\\frac{1}{n(n+2)} = \\frac{1}{2}\\left(\\frac{1}{n} - \\frac{1}{n+2}\\right)$","formula":""},{"title":"计算过程","content":"$x \\cdot \\frac{1}{2} \\left( (1 - \\frac{1}{3}) + (\\frac{1}{3} - \\frac{1}{5}) + \\dots + (\\frac{1}{2023} - \\frac{1}{2025}) \\right) = 1$\n\n$\\frac{x}{2} \\left( 1 - \\frac{1}{2025} \\right) = 1 \\Rightarrow \\frac{x}{2} \\cdot \\frac{2024}{2025} = 1$","formula":"x = \\frac{2025}{1012}"}]},"id":"t26-train-1"},"__N_SSG":true}